1
00:00:11,291 --> 00:00:13,208
[SAYA]
Who the hell was that?

2
00:00:13,291 --> 00:00:16,041
[HAJIME]
Have a good day!

3
00:00:16,125 --> 00:00:18,208
See ya later!

4
00:00:21,875 --> 00:00:22,833
[HAJIME]
Uh.

5
00:00:25,125 --> 00:00:28,541
[TEACHER A]
Endo. Endo.

6
00:00:28,625 --> 00:00:30,000
You okay?

7
00:00:31,208 --> 00:00:32,791
[SAYA]
"See you later"?

8
00:00:32,875 --> 00:00:34,416
"See you later"?

9
00:00:34,500 --> 00:00:35,916
[GIRL A]
Hey, Saya!

10
00:00:38,666 --> 00:00:40,416
[SAYA]
Unforgivable!

11
00:00:40,500 --> 00:00:42,958
Yo, Coconuts, wanna
come game at my place?

12
00:00:43,041 --> 00:00:44,291
Sounds fun.

13
00:00:44,375 --> 00:00:46,583
Cool, you wanna play
with us, Saya?

14
00:00:47,666 --> 00:00:51,916
No, I can't today. I have
afterschool activities.

15
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:53,291
[TO]
Huh?

16
00:00:53,375 --> 00:00:57,625
Hold on. Since when did you
have afterschool stuff?

17
00:00:57,708 --> 00:01:02,666
♪


18
00:02:28,041 --> 00:02:29,666
[SAYA]
I don't have time for games.

19
00:02:29,750 --> 00:02:33,041
I need to find out
who that hussy was.

20
00:02:33,125 --> 00:02:35,041
I bet she's some
conniving she-devil

21
00:02:35,125 --> 00:02:40,083
who tricked Coconuts
into staying with him.

22
00:02:40,166 --> 00:02:42,000
But wait, if that's it,

23
00:02:42,083 --> 00:02:44,583
then she might have already
gained complete control

24
00:02:44,666 --> 00:02:46,083
over his body and soul!

25
00:02:46,166 --> 00:02:48,000
[HAJIME]
You can call me "Mommy."

26
00:02:48,083 --> 00:02:49,541
[KOKONOTSU]
Mommy!

27
00:02:49,625 --> 00:02:51,458
[gasps] I wonder...

28
00:02:51,541 --> 00:02:55,333
Uh! Shut up, brain!
There's no way that's true!

29
00:02:56,791 --> 00:03:00,083
Hey, you! Can I
please come in?

30
00:03:05,916 --> 00:03:10,208
[HAJIME snoring]

31
00:03:10,291 --> 00:03:12,125
She's asleep?

32
00:03:12,208 --> 00:03:14,625
Um, excuse me?

33
00:03:14,708 --> 00:03:15,750
[HAJIME]

34
00:03:17,375 --> 00:03:19,875
Hi! I'm awake!

35
00:03:19,958 --> 00:03:23,625
[HAJIME screams]

36
00:03:23,708 --> 00:03:27,458
[HAJIME]
Owie, my poor noggin!

37
00:03:29,041 --> 00:03:31,125
Whoa! A customer.

38
00:03:31,208 --> 00:03:32,666
Hi, welcome!

39
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:34,541
Ah, nailed it!

40
00:03:34,625 --> 00:03:37,125
I've been waiting all day
to welcome someone.

41
00:03:37,208 --> 00:03:39,583
Uh. I'm not following.

42
00:03:39,666 --> 00:03:40,916
[HAJIME]
Hm?

43
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:43,416
Oh, are you maybe one
of the manager's friends?

44
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:44,916
[SAYA]
Maybe.

45
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:48,458
Well then, I'm Hajime Owari,
the new part-time worker!

46
00:03:48,541 --> 00:03:49,500
You are?

47
00:03:49,583 --> 00:03:51,541
Yes indeed-y,
I was just hired!

48
00:03:51,625 --> 00:03:54,208
I work during the day while
the manager is at school.

49
00:03:54,291 --> 00:03:55,750
[SAYA]
That jerk!

50
00:03:55,833 --> 00:03:59,208
I can't believe he hired some
random woman off the street!

51
00:03:59,291 --> 00:04:02,000
He's going to pay dearly
for this insult!

52
00:04:02,083 --> 00:04:04,958
Kokonotsu sure has
it rough, huh?

53
00:04:05,041 --> 00:04:07,208
Wait, are you leaving?

54
00:04:07,291 --> 00:04:10,958
Excuse me. Wasn't there
something you wanted to buy?

55
00:04:11,041 --> 00:04:13,583
No, I didn't come here
to buy anything.

56
00:04:13,666 --> 00:04:16,333
Oh, so you came to
see the manager?

57
00:04:16,416 --> 00:04:19,583
Ah, I get it. You must
be his girlfriend!

58
00:04:22,125 --> 00:04:24,250
Who? Me? Him? A couple?

59
00:04:24,333 --> 00:04:27,333
That's crazy talk! Whatever!

60
00:04:27,416 --> 00:04:30,916
But maybe I should buy
something after all.

61
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,125
[HAJIME]
Let's see.

62
00:04:32,208 --> 00:04:35,250
A snack that'd be good
for his girlfriend.

63
00:04:35,333 --> 00:04:37,791
Found one! It's perfect!

64
00:04:37,875 --> 00:04:40,666
This is Roll Candy.
It's only 35 yen!

65
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:43,041
But why this snack?

66
00:04:43,125 --> 00:04:44,791
Well, the manager said,

67
00:04:44,875 --> 00:04:46,916
"This one is pretty
popular right now."

68
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:51,000
He's so knowledgeable!
Not to mention dedicated.

69
00:04:51,083 --> 00:04:52,291
Uh, thank you!

70
00:04:52,375 --> 00:04:54,583
Oh, you're already
opening it up?

71
00:04:54,666 --> 00:04:56,291
Let's see.

72
00:04:56,375 --> 00:04:59,750
So, like, is it supposed to
be rolled up or whatever?

73
00:04:59,833 --> 00:05:01,333
I'm confused.

74
00:05:01,416 --> 00:05:04,583
I think maybe you just eat it
all in one bite or something.

75
00:05:04,666 --> 00:05:06,583
Huh?

76
00:05:06,666 --> 00:05:09,583
Wait, then does that mean
the paper is edible?

77
00:05:09,666 --> 00:05:11,958
I'm not entirely sure.

78
00:05:13,250 --> 00:05:14,500
[SAYA]
For real?

79
00:05:14,583 --> 00:05:16,000
How the heck can you not
know what you're selling?

80
00:05:16,083 --> 00:05:19,708
Look, I'm sorry, but this
is my first day, after all!

81
00:05:19,791 --> 00:05:20,708
Hold the phone!

82
00:05:20,791 --> 00:05:22,083
If you're so close
to the manager,

83
00:05:22,166 --> 00:05:24,291
then shouldn't you know
about that <i>dagashi</i> ?

84
00:05:24,375 --> 00:05:25,416
[SAYA]
Uh.

85
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:28,333
I mean, yeah,
we're totally close.

86
00:05:28,416 --> 00:05:31,833
Okay! Well, I'm gonna unroll it.

87
00:05:31,916 --> 00:05:33,166
Are you ready?

88
00:05:33,250 --> 00:05:34,291
[HAJIME]
Yes!

89
00:05:35,333 --> 00:05:37,250
[BOTH]
Whoa, candy!

90
00:05:37,333 --> 00:05:40,375
And by the looks
of it, it peels off.

91
00:05:40,458 --> 00:05:42,875
Well, good thing you
didn't eat the paper.

92
00:05:43,916 --> 00:05:44,750
[gasps]

93
00:05:44,833 --> 00:05:46,833
I figured out how to eat it!

94
00:05:47,916 --> 00:05:49,583
[SAYA gasps]

95
00:05:49,666 --> 00:05:50,916
[HAJIME]
You grab it here.

96
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:52,125
[SAYA]
Wait, what?

97
00:05:52,208 --> 00:05:55,125
[HAJIME]
Put the tip in your mouth.

98
00:05:55,208 --> 00:05:59,583
Okay. I'll hold onto this end.

99
00:05:59,666 --> 00:06:00,750
Are you ready?

100
00:06:00,833 --> 00:06:02,291
[SAYA]
Mh-hm.

101
00:06:02,375 --> 00:06:04,333
[HAJIME]
Go!

102
00:06:10,875 --> 00:06:11,833
Whoa, we did it!

103
00:06:11,916 --> 00:06:13,083
[SAYA chuckles]

104
00:06:13,166 --> 00:06:15,791
But I guess you could've
done it all by yourself.

105
00:06:15,875 --> 00:06:17,958
[SAYA]
Yeah, I could.

106
00:06:18,041 --> 00:06:21,458
[BOTH laughing]

107
00:06:21,541 --> 00:06:23,666
Hey, Saya!

108
00:06:23,750 --> 00:06:27,291
I didn't know you were
here, but welcome.

109
00:06:27,375 --> 00:06:29,250
Hi! Welcome back!

110
00:06:29,333 --> 00:06:31,041
Thanks, how was your first day?

111
00:06:31,125 --> 00:06:33,416
Ah! It wore me out!

112
00:06:33,500 --> 00:06:35,583
At least <i>dagashi</i> are
pretty interesting.

113
00:06:35,666 --> 00:06:37,375
[KOKONOTSU]
Was it busy?

114
00:06:37,458 --> 00:06:39,875
At any rate,
I'm glad you had fun.

115
00:06:39,958 --> 00:06:42,500
You can take off if you
want. I'll watch things.

116
00:06:42,583 --> 00:06:44,541
[HAJIME]
Yay, freedom!

117
00:06:44,625 --> 00:06:46,333
Thanks, manager!

118
00:06:46,416 --> 00:06:48,333
[SAYA] She doesn't seem
like a bad person,

119
00:06:48,416 --> 00:06:50,583
so I guess she's cool, for now.

120
00:06:50,666 --> 00:06:53,416
[HAJIME] So would it be
okay if I go take a bath?

121
00:06:54,791 --> 00:06:57,541
Uh. I didn't take
one yesterday.

122
00:06:57,625 --> 00:07:00,791
Huh? I'd prefer you
bathe every day.

123
00:07:00,875 --> 00:07:02,500
[HAJIME]
Okie dokie!

124
00:07:02,583 --> 00:07:04,166
Coconuts?

125
00:07:04,250 --> 00:07:06,458
Isn't she a part-time worker?

126
00:07:06,541 --> 00:07:08,958
Yeah, but she's
a live-in worker,

127
00:07:09,041 --> 00:07:10,625
which really helps a lot.

128
00:07:10,708 --> 00:07:13,708
Ah, that makes sense.

129
00:07:13,791 --> 00:07:16,875
What is wrong with you?!

130
00:07:16,958 --> 00:07:19,458
[KOKONOTSU]
What'd I do?

131
00:07:19,541 --> 00:07:22,458
[TO] Man, it's been a hot
minute since Coconuts and I

132
00:07:22,541 --> 00:07:24,875
have had a chance to
play "Debt Collector."

133
00:07:26,375 --> 00:07:29,458
I've gotten good at it,
wait until he sees.

134
00:07:29,541 --> 00:07:31,541
Well, here goes nothin'.

135
00:07:31,625 --> 00:07:32,875
[chuckles]

136
00:07:32,958 --> 00:07:35,625
In this kind of game,
you have to start strong.

137
00:07:35,708 --> 00:07:38,500
If you don't commit, then
you risk looking stupid,

138
00:07:38,583 --> 00:07:41,083
and no one wants to look stupid.

139
00:07:41,166 --> 00:07:42,666
Time to strike!

140
00:07:42,750 --> 00:07:44,500
Hey, Shikada.

141
00:07:44,583 --> 00:07:48,250
it's time for you to pay
the piper, ya filthy animal.

142
00:07:48,333 --> 00:07:53,000
If you can't pony up the cash,
then I'm afraid you've left us--

143
00:07:54,208 --> 00:07:55,916
[HAJIME]
Uh.

144
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,500
[TO]
Oh, crap!

145
00:07:57,583 --> 00:08:01,125
I just spoke to a total stranger
in my best mobster impression!

146
00:08:01,208 --> 00:08:03,291
Goodbye dignity!

147
00:08:03,375 --> 00:08:07,583
Why doesn't life have
a rewind button? Why?

148
00:08:07,666 --> 00:08:09,250
[HAJIME]
Oh, no.

149
00:08:09,333 --> 00:08:13,875
You're saying, Kokonotsu
owes you some money?

150
00:08:13,958 --> 00:08:17,250
[TO]
No way. I can't believe my ears.

151
00:08:17,333 --> 00:08:20,875
Is she actually playing
along with me?

152
00:08:20,958 --> 00:08:23,416
Um, he stepped out
for the moment.

153
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:26,083
Could you come back later?

154
00:08:26,166 --> 00:08:28,750
[TO] She's being kind enough
to go along with it.

155
00:08:28,833 --> 00:08:32,208
I need to get it together,
or else she'll feel stupid, too!

156
00:08:35,625 --> 00:08:37,458
[TO]
"Come back later," eh?

157
00:08:37,541 --> 00:08:42,375
I'm tired of that crap excuse.
I ain't goin' back empty handed.

158
00:08:42,458 --> 00:08:44,500
Um. I'm sorry?

159
00:08:44,583 --> 00:08:47,750
I guess you'll just have to do.

160
00:08:47,833 --> 00:08:51,500
Yeah, like pay with your body.

161
00:08:51,583 --> 00:08:53,916
[HAJIME]
Pay you with my body?

162
00:08:55,708 --> 00:08:57,041
[screams]

163
00:08:57,125 --> 00:08:58,708
Spare me, I beg of you!

164
00:08:58,791 --> 00:08:59,833
No one would want me!

165
00:08:59,916 --> 00:09:02,000
My lifestyle choices
are iffy at best!

166
00:09:02,083 --> 00:09:05,666
[TO] We don't care.
We ain't runnin' a charity.

167
00:09:05,750 --> 00:09:07,250
I'll do anything!

168
00:09:07,333 --> 00:09:11,916
Okay, fine. I'm feeling
generous, so...

169
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:14,000
[HAJIME]
Thank you.

170
00:09:14,083 --> 00:09:17,750
But in return, I want you
to do somethin' funny.

171
00:09:17,833 --> 00:09:20,250
Me? Do something funny?

172
00:09:30,750 --> 00:09:33,625
Jeez, what the--?
Where are they?

173
00:09:33,708 --> 00:09:38,125
Can't find my glasses.
Where could they have gone?

174
00:09:38,208 --> 00:09:40,083
Oh, here they are.

175
00:09:40,166 --> 00:09:42,041
[TO]
No way!

176
00:09:42,125 --> 00:09:44,666
Yay! Now I can see!

177
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:46,166
[HAJIME chuckles]

178
00:09:46,250 --> 00:09:47,833
[TO] That's the chocolate
glasses snack you always find

179
00:09:47,916 --> 00:09:50,208
near registers at
the grocery store!

180
00:09:50,291 --> 00:09:52,833
This lady is good!

181
00:09:52,916 --> 00:09:55,000
Wow, that's funny!

182
00:09:55,083 --> 00:09:57,583
[HAJIME]
Not only can I see,

183
00:09:57,666 --> 00:10:01,375
I can also... have a snack!

184
00:10:01,458 --> 00:10:02,375
[TO]
Ah!

185
00:10:02,458 --> 00:10:04,500
Functional and yummy!

186
00:10:04,583 --> 00:10:07,208
I wanna do it, too!
My turn, my turn!

187
00:10:07,291 --> 00:10:08,333
Did you like that?

188
00:10:08,416 --> 00:10:11,125
[TO]
Yeah! I'll take ten, please!

189
00:10:11,208 --> 00:10:13,458
[TO laughing]

190
00:10:13,541 --> 00:10:16,833
My friends are gonna
laugh so hard, right?

191
00:10:16,916 --> 00:10:19,208
Thank you so much! See ya later!

192
00:10:19,291 --> 00:10:20,875
Uh, bye!

193
00:10:22,416 --> 00:10:24,458
[HAJIME sighs]

194
00:10:24,541 --> 00:10:27,208
Wow, I survived.

195
00:10:27,291 --> 00:10:29,458
[KOKONOTSU]
Hey, I'm back!

196
00:10:32,541 --> 00:10:35,250
[KOKONOTSU] What's wrong,
Miss Hajime? What happened?

197
00:10:35,333 --> 00:10:36,458
[HAJIME]
Kokonotsu.

198
00:10:36,541 --> 00:10:38,208
Uh, what's up?

199
00:10:38,291 --> 00:10:42,916
I promise... I'll
protect your shop, okay?

200
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,916
Uh, wha...?

201
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:48,416
I'll protect it!

202
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:53,458
♪


203
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,041
[HAJIME]
Next time:

204
00:12:20,125 --> 00:12:22,416
"Internets, Super Ball, and..."

205
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:24,833
You just leave
everything to me, okay?

